OL,13,     Gthird visit of the week, at the
OL,14,     GDomo Boutique Hotel in
OL,15,     GBirmingham. Helen's dazzled by
OL,16,     Gthe decor, but trouble brews over
OL,17,     Ga caffeine conundrum.
