OL,4,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAt The Crown Inn in Norfolk, Lisa
OL,6,     Gand Neil hope that their historic
OL,7,     Gsetting will bag them the B&B
OL,8,     Gcrown. But there are 'paneful'
OL,9,     Gobservations about the windows
OL,10,     Gand a lorry-load of noise.
OL,11,G2030FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GOn the final day, the B&Bers
OL,13,     Gdiscover how much they've been
OL,14,     Gpaid. Comments about curtains and
OL,15,     Goff-colour feedback about bedding
OL,16,     Gleave some hosts open-mouthed,
OL,17,     Gbefore the winner is crowned.
